<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Hand-authored regression fixture modelled on the Microsoft Threat Modeling
  Tool 2016 (schema Version 4.3) .NET DataContract export. It is deliberately
  small but covers every branch the importer walks: each stencil shape, an
  unknown GenericTypeId, an out-of-scope element, a nil element name, a border
  boundary, a line boundary, a connector to an excluded element, entity-escaped
  and multi-line text, a threat that falls back to its TypeId category, a threat
  that falls back to its Properties priority, and a threat with an empty title.

  The expected import result is pinned in tmt-4.3-sample.expected.yaml.
-->
